title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 33] Post-Punk, Darkwave
description:
Here's my early Christmas gift to the collectors of 80s rarities (in particular my dear friend Edward), however stay tuned cause I will post big time in the holiday season. To fans of more mainstream, new wavish 80's, don't be disappointed if these are not complegtely up your alley as there would be some great torrents for you too. This torrents includes:


Bad Baby - Bad Baby [1985]

Cuddly Toys - Guillotine Theatre [1980]

Marquis de Sade - Rue de Siam [1981]

Persona Non Grata - Our Shade of Sin [1984]
